                        <rs type="person" ref="pe__walter_von_seuseneck_QGW_II_I_1076"><roleName type="kin" corresp="pe__dorothea_QGW_II_I_867">Bruder</roleName> Walthern von
                        Seusenekk</rs></rs>.</rs>
            </p></div><div type="seal"><p><rs type="event" ref="ev__QGW_II_I_868"><rs type="fn" role="witness">Besiegelt mit
